    ItemEntangledChalice.FluidHandler

    public class FluidContainerItemWrapperWithSimulation
extends org.cyclops.cyclopscore.capability.fluid.FluidHandlerItemCapacity
    Safer version of FluidHandlerItemCapacity that makes sure that simulated fluidstacks are not filled/drained without simulation. This must be used for tanks that are omni-present, meaning that their fluid data is independent of the itemstack. This only works for containers that do NOT swap their item when filling/draining.
